Hilal Browser: redirect About Dialog and Help links to Hilal custom domains

Modify the href attributes inside aboutDialog.xhtml to point to Hilal's
official website (hilal.gkdevstudio.org) and GitHub repository
(github.com/vastsea0/hilal-browser).
Also configure getHelpLinkURL in utilityOverlay.js to skip topic appending
when custom Hilal/GitHub domains are used.

